es<br></li><li>11 playable levels including two survival and a speed challenge<br></li><li>22 original and intense tracks for more than sixty minutes of listening</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/de977ec481247b71fb299372c793bf3d.poster.avif?t=1631105095\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/de977ec481247b71fb299372c793bf3d.webm?t=1631105095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/de977ec481247b71fb299372c793bf3d.mp4?t=1631105095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GEAR</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose between two different spaceships<br></li><li>Enhance your weapons by collecting money and spend it at checkpoints<br></li><li>Replay any unlocked levels to strengthen your arsenal</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INCENTIVES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>19 Steam successes <br></li><li>Fight in hard mode for more challenge and to unlock hidden bosses  <br></li><li>Leaderboard<br></li><li>Full gamepad control</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/efbb280e7d96a44c6ad1d96240db4a2c.poster.avif?t=1631105095\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/efbb280e7d96a44c6ad1d96240db4a2c.webm?t=1631105095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857900/extras/efbb280e7d96a44c6ad1d96240db4a2c.mp4?t=1631105095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
